SUMMARY:Cassidy and The Music live at Montclair Brewery
DESCRIPTION:World-class vocalist Cassidy Catanzaro is primed to grace our taproom stage with her mesmerizing voice that can seamlessly transition from powerful ballads to energetic anthems. She is a Grammy-nominated and award-winning songwriter\, formerly the lead singer for the band Antigone Rising\, the first all-female band in history to tour with the Rolling Stones. Cassidy has made an indelible mark on the global music scene. She has appeared on The Today Show\, The Tonight Show\, and Breakfast With The Arts. \n$5 cover charge per person that goes directly to the artists. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
