SUMMARY:Chantilly Live at Montclair Brewery
DESCRIPTION:Chantilly Mers is a musical blend of her life’s journey. From her Hawaii island upbringing of roots reggae\, to soul\, blues\, R&B and jazz influences from her many years in Harlem\, NYC. Her warmth and spirit gathers people in close\, while her voice carries the ache and beauty of what it means to be human — reminding us it’s okay to feel\, to fall apart\, and be put back together by Love. \n$5 cover charge per person that goes directly to the artists. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
