SUMMARY:Easter Paint & Create
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an afternoon of creativity and fun! For the adults\, it’s a classic sip & paint—while the kids enjoy their own paint & fun experience. \nCelebrate with us the Saturday before Easter at our second Paint & Sip event\, where everyone is welcome! \n$40 per adult — includes a canvas\, all painting materials\, and a cocktail\n$25 per child — includes a canvas and all painting materials \nBring your creativity and come make some colorful memories together! 🎨✨ \nThe ticket price of $25 covers the child’s ticket plus the $25 deducted from the $40 adult ticket. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
